window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When an unexpected betrayal steals our sanctuary, only unity will save us.</p> <p>I trusted Michael and he betrayed us.</p> <p>With our sanctuary destroyed, we're on the run. Again.</p> <p>Shem and his watchers' step into the role of protectors once again but keeping a whole colony safe topside won't be easy.</p> <p>New threats stalk both day and night. The rules have changed.</p> <p>Time is running out. And for some of us, this journey will be the end of the road.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
